text: Mathias Jamtvedt (14 August 1922 - 15 October 2000) was a Norwegian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1922 births Category:2000 deaths Category:Norwegian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Norway Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Skien
